<h1> Store Edit </h1>
<p>To make changes to your current store information, please fill out the form below. </p>

<p> *NOTICE*: by filling out this form you will be changing the store information for all users associated with this store. If you are attempting to change your store to a different existing store, you will need to register a new user account with your new store's ID.</p>

<form action='/stores/<%=@store.id%>' method='POST'>
<input id="hidden" type="hidden" name="_method" value="patch">
<p>Update Store Name:<input type="text" name="name"></p>
<p>Update Location:<input type="text" name="location"></p>
<input type="submit" value="update">
</form>